{"id":42,"title":"*问：**简述Go语言中defer, panic, recover的作用和关系。","slug":"*问：**简述Go语言中defer,-panic,-recover的作用和关系。-1766595046","excerpt":"","content":"**参考回答：**`defer`、`panic`、`recover`共同构成了Go处理异常情况的机制。`defer`语句用于延迟执行一段代码（通常是清理收尾动作），无论函数正常返回还是发生宕机，都能确保`defer`的代码被执行。`panic`用于在遇到无法继续的错误状况时中止当前函数的执行，并向上抛出运行时错误（类似抛出异常），最终（如果未被捕获）导致程序崩溃。`recover`则是配合`defer`使用的一个函数，用来捕获从`panic`抛出的错误，使程序从宕机状态恢复。一般的用法是在一个defer的匿名函数中调用`recover()`，获取panic的错误信息并处理，从而阻止程序崩溃。需要注意，`recover`只有在defer调用中才能截获panic。通过这三个关键字，Go实现了基本的异常处理：正常流程用错误返回值处理，严重异常情况下用panic中断，并允许上层通过recover捕获处理。\n\n","tags":"","categories":"","cover_image_url":"","access_level":"PUBLIC","status":"PUBLISHED","published_at":"2025-12-25T00:50:46.243372+08:00","last_edited_at":"2025-12-25T00:50:46.243372+08:00","notion_page_id":"1f95d23c-2eec-802b-9360-d2ff8de6bb07","notion_last_edit":"2025-05-20T05:56:00Z","author_id":1,"author":{"id":1,"username":"admin","email":"admin@example.com","role":"ADMIN","is_verified":true,"is_active":true,"avatar":"","bio":"","last_login_at":"2025-12-20T00:47:21.462367+08:00","email_verified_at":"2026-03-09T22:24:23.810219+08:00","created_at":"2025-12-19T09:00:38.872854652Z","updated_at":"2026-03-09T22:24:24.010602+08:00","is_admin":true},"stats":{"id":42,"blog_post_id":42,"blog_post":{"id":0,"title":"","slug":"","excerpt":"","content":"","tags":"","categories":"","cover_image_url":"","access_level":"","status":"","author_id":0,"author":{"id":0,"username":"","email":"","role":"","is_verified":false,"is_active":false,"avatar":"","bio":"","created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","updated_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","is_admin":false},"created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","updated_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z"},"view_count":0,"like_count":0,"share_count":0,"comment_count":0,"created_at":"2025-12-25T00:54:02.601584+08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-25T00:54:02.601584+08:00"},"created_at":"2025-12-25T00:50:46.243372+08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-25T00:50:46.243372+08:00"}